<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>FliQ - 명함 공유</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/pretendard@1.3.6/dist/web/static/pretendard.css"
    />
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        width: 100vw;
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        font-family: "Pretendard", Arial, sans-serif;
      }

      #container {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 60px;
      }

      header {
        height: 80px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding-left: 40px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid lightgray;
      }

      main {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100%;
        padding: 1rem;
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-20px);
        transition: opacity 1s ease, transform 1s ease;
      }

      .visible {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }

      .title {
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: black;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        line-height: 30px;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 300;
        color: black;
        letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        font-family: "Pretendard", Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 30px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 400px) {
        .title {
          font-size: 30px;
          line-height: 24px;
        }

        .subtitle {
          font-size: 18px;
          line-height: 24px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="container">
      <header>FliQ - 터치 한 번으로 빠르게 명함 전달</header>
      <main id="content">
        <div>
          <span class="title">알 수 없는 요청입니다.</span>
          <span class="subtitle"></br>링크를 한번 더 확인해주세요</span>
        </div>
      </main>
    </div>
    <script>
      window.onload = function () {
        const content = document.getElementById("content");
        setTimeout(() => {
          content.classList.add("visible");
        }, 300);
      };
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
